See INSTALL for informaion about how to install.


If you face problems with enabled gzipped buffered output
(ob_start("ob_gzhandler"); in maincore.php): This is not a Pro/Review issue.
Pro/Review uses PHP-Fusion review class.


If you need to protect your files from direct review specifying filenames
directly try this simple .htaccess file in your reviews/ directory.

--begin
Order deny,allow
Deny from all
Allow from 127.0.0.1

ErrorDocument 403 "<p><b>No Way!</b>
--end


(Es gibt auch eine deutsche INSTALL.de)
